(1, 'level-3-award-in-education-training-aet-course', '2345234', 'Level 3: Award in Education & Training (AET) Course 1', 'Level 3 Award in Education and Training AET formerly known as PTLLS Course is designed to give people the knowledge and confidence to teach adult in any specialty subject area. This course is suitable for someone who wants to work as a teacher/trainer/tutor in further education. Russbridge Academy are delighted to offer Level 3 Award in Education and Training (AET) qualification via Distance Learning / Online or Face to Face Classroom based or Live Zoom classroom course. This Level 3 AET is a direct replacement qualification of Level 3/4 Preparing to Teach in the Lifelong Learning Sector (PTLLS) course sometimes also referred to colloquially as “PETALS” since 2011.\r\n\r\nLevel 3 Award in Education and Training AET Course is an initial teacher training qualification, is also a Regulated Qualifications Framework RQF and OFQUAL regulated. This course is best suits for those who are new to teaching, or wishing to start out a teacher / trainer or currently teaching in England, Wales, Scotland and Ireland. Level 3 Award in Education and Training AET /PTLLS is designed to give people the knowledge and confidence to teach any adult people in any subject area and certifying people to teach at a nationally accredited standard.', '234c1938ac16565e2f21ce088dba6c47e88586c2f66a671e2e2b89a5e79bed17bd31243c0ae25db8d1e4fe3ce97dba9903919432bb0022c5db5e075665759889.jpg', '2024-09-10 16:39:50', NULL),
(2, '234-2', '234', 'Level 4: Certificate in Education & Training (CET) Course', 'Level 4 Certificate in Education and Training CET course is a teaching qualification for people who work or wish to work as teachers and is a QCF qualification and regulated by Ofqual. This Course is a replacement of Level 4 Certificate in Teaching in the Lifelong Learning Sector (CTLLS) course. All candidates, whether pre-service (Currently not working) or in-service (Currently working) must have access to 30 hours of teaching in order to complete the award. This qualification is suitable for those delivering teaching and training in any learning discipline eg University, College, Training provider, any organisation or Company either paid, Volunteer, full time, part time or any kind of teaching.', '6ba0f906205f853c4638478255a7e1a764a75809f58b03d823ce34ba719ddf1dad3791f87a0cfe4d779ef0c9bfa30aa5cedec30a8be06114baf89d38414f539c.jpg', '2024-09-10 17:56:58', NULL);
